http://github.com/concord-consortium/sproutcore_datasource_part1

Adding dataSource tests to Tomas Svarovsky's SproutCore DataSource sample app:

  http://www.svarovsky-tomas.com/sproutcore-datasource.html
  http://github.com/fluke777/sproutcore_datasource_part1

Some of the work adapted from http://github.com/knowuh/raclette

Gem requirements: sinatra, thin, json-pure

Tested on ruby 1.9.2 head and SproutCore master.

Starting the sinatra server:

  cd server
  ruby demo.rb -p 9393

Starting the SproutCore development server

  sc-server

Running the dataSource tests:

  fetch:  http://localhost:4020/md/en/current/tests/data_sources/sinatra/fetch.html
  create: http://localhost:4020/md/en/current/tests/data_sources/sinatra/create.html

